    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and some fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some minor staining, though the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it may require some upcoming maintenance or minor repairs to address parts worn from high mileage. It's a reliable option for someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle who doesn't mind some cosmetic and mechanical imperfections.",
