      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a level of meticulous care that is truly unrivaled in the pre-owned market. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning driver. We invite you to inspect a vehicle that sets the benchmark for excellence and represents a rare opportunity to own a masterfully kept classic.",
