    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You are going to absolutely love this car! It is in truly spectacular shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows in every detail. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
