      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless E46 M3, maintained to a concours standard with an emphasis on mechanical longevity and visceral performance. The S54 powerplant features a fully overhauled VANOS system and updated rod bearings, ensuring the high-revving 3.2L inline-six operates at peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the subframe mounting points to preserve torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M differential lock. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains factory paint depth with zero road rash or imperfections. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking an uncompromised driving dynamic.",
